snippet.title: Dragon Ball FighterZ - XB1/PS4/PC - Bardock (Full character Intro +  release date)
snippet.description:
Goku’s family extends with Bardock.
Expect a great dramatic scene between the Saiyan warrior and lord Frieza ;)
